TopicTitle: Mun and Back with only toridial tanks- Apollo style Pic heavy

Articles.Content:
Self explnatory. An entry for the [I <3 Round-8 Challenge.](https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/115659-The-I?p=1839079&viewfull=1#post1839079)

RIP our little gold friend, you shall be missed.

Ten minutes of silence while we go over the memorial mission.

(no RCS involved in this mission!)
